---
source: src/core/learn.rs
assertion: learn commands use persisted observation ledgers
schema:
  agenda: ee.learn.agenda.v1
  uncertainty: ee.learn.uncertainty.v1
  summary: ee.learn.summary.v1
  experiment_proposal: ee.learn.experiment_proposal.v1
contracts:
  - empty ledger returns zero items in agenda
  - single-topic cluster with fewer than 2 observations has low confidence
  - multi-topic sessions group by tag co-occurrence and semantic similarity
  - uncertainty is computed from rule-confidence distributions
  - summary aggregates observation counts and feedback statistics
  - experiment propose persists candidates to curation queue
  - determinism: same observations yield same proposed candidate IDs
evidence:
  - learning_observations.id
  - learning_observations.signal
  - learning_observations.measurement_name
  - feedback_events.signal
  - curation_candidates.workspace_id
  - curation_candidates.source_id
